<br>
This same Strategy Guide also lists some rules of etiquette concerning camps:<br>
Pg. 239, Paragraph 1<br>
&quot;If a party is already at a spawn point when you arrive, respect their camp and don't pull from that area. Especially if they are in a room, everything in that room is 'theirs.'<br>
