Verant breaks their own rules as fast as they make them. It's up to the players to make and enforce rules acceptable to them. That's why it's common courtesy to do a camp check in an area you just arrived in. It's common courtesy to not loot something you didn't kill. It's common courtesy to shout &quot;Train!&quot; if you're the one pulling it to zone.<br>
<br>
